Some enemies will display a [!] sign on top of their
heads before they do a particular strong move.
If the sign is red,it's probably a physical attack.

avoided and require some deeper knowledge of the move
itself if you wish to survive it.

The same is true for elements.

Try water or ice based attacks instead.

Try to mix fast moves together to act before your
enemies or try to mix a fast one with a slow one if
you feel like you wish to do your fast move slower.
